EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
AZORES TO CANARY ISLANDS.
DNC 01, DNC 08.
38 FOOT S/V ROAMER, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
OVERDUE TERCEIRA (38-43N 027-14W)
TO CANARY ISLANDS (28-06N 015-24W).
